f. Chairman of the Committee on International Relations of the City Council of Manila;
g. Chairman of the Committee on Environmental Protection, Ecological Preservation and Sanitation of the City Council of Manila;
h. Chairman of the Manila Chinatown Barangay Organization;
i. All Councilors from District II of Manila;
j. All Councilors from District III of Manila;
