l. Representative from the Real Property Owner's Association in Chinatown (Binondo Area);
m. Representative from the Chinese Educational Institutions in Chinatown (Binondo Area);
n. Representative from the Property Development and Investors;
o. Academic Consultant on Filipino-Chinese Culture; and
p. Federation of Filipino-Chinese Chambers of Commerce and Industry.”

SEC. 3. Effectivity Clause. — This Ordinance shall take effect upon its approval.
