b) For the Second Offense – a fine of Four Thousand Pesos (PhP 4,000.00) with recommendation by the MHD to the BPLO for a Cease-and-Desist Order on the establishment's operations to take effect forthwith;
c) For the Third Offense – a fine of Five Thousand Pesos (PhP 5,000.00) with recommendation by the MHD to the BPLO for a Closure Order on the establishment to immediately effect a permanent closure thereof.

